description:
On an all new Unqualified, Anna and Sim welcome Denis Leary (RESCUE ME, SEX&DRUGS&ROCK&ROLL) to chat about working with Clint Eastwood (13:00), James Woods pickup attempts (16:00), and accepting praise as Willem Dafoe (30:00).

After the break, they play a round of Deal Breakers (39:00) and How Would You proceed? (46:00) before calling David (53:30) who's trying to save his relationship that has a fast approaching expiration date.

 

Pick up Denis Leary's new book Why We Don't Suck today!
